message: Hi Bob, I hope you're doing well. I’m excited to offer you an exclusive product that I believe can add significant value. Based on its unique features and benefits, I’d like to offer it to you for $30000. Let me know if this proposal works for you or if you have any questions!
Hi Alice, thanks for your offer. However, $30000 is beyond my budget. I'm interested in the product, but I can only go up to $5000. Let me know if this works for you.
